dataset.name: NYMEX Natural Gas (Henry Hub), March 2025 (NGH2025)
dataset.description:
Contract Size: 10,000 million British thermal units (mmBtu).

Deliverable Good: Natural Gas meeting the specifications set forth in the FERC-approved tariff of Sabine Pipe Line Company as then in effect at the time of delivery shall be deliverable in satisfaction of futures contract delivery obligations.

Tick Size: $0.001 per MMBtu

Pricing Unit: U.S. dollars and cents per mmBtu.

Columns: Open, High, Low, Settle, Volume, Previous Day Open Interest. Note that Open Interest is always reported for the previous trading day, to avoid lookahead bias.
